Package com.dufuna.berlin.juwonadeyemi.lekki.model

Class LekkiProperty

java.lang.Object
com.dufuna.berlin.juwonadeyemi.lekki.model.LekkiProperty
public class LekkiProperty extends Object
Represents a Lekki Property with various attributes. This class provides methods to get and set property details.
